rComments: Lecture-based. Will test you on smaller details in the final but she's fair. Great at making the material digestable and interesting.

Eliana Gonzales-Vigil is a prof who cares about her students. She makes lectures interactive and fun. For her tests, it's sufficient to study her lecture slides. The tests and assignments are fair and relatively straight forward.
